snippet.title: Live Meditation With Gurudev | World Meditation Day 21st Dec 2024
snippet.description:
The world is coming together on the 21st of December 2024 on the occasion of World Meditation Day to meditate with Gurudev Sri Sri Ravi Shankar, this is going to be the most historic and largest meditation event. You don't want to miss out!

About #Gurudev - 
The world is coming together on the 21st of December 2024 to celebrate World Meditation Day 
World-renowned humanitarian, spiritual leader, and an ambassador of peace and human values. Through his life and work, Gurudev Sri Sri Ravi Shankar has inspired millions around the world with a vision of a stress-free and peaceful world. Gurudev founded The Art of Living, a non-profit organization that is engaged in stress-management and service initiatives across the world.

Learn Sudarshan Kriya the world's most powerful breathing technique: https://aoliv.in/learnsudarshankriya

Do Like, Comment, Share & Subscribe to the channel!

Subscribe to Gurudev's Channel: 
https://youtube.com/srisri

🎧Listen to Gurudev on Spotify:
Talks - https://open.spotify.com/show/75Wx1ZyzhReLUFI6lgQGTS
Meditations - https://open.spotify.com/show/6INVWvhJjH9t88iURiN2xf

Follow Gurudev on Instagram: 
https://instagram.com/srisriravishankar

Like Gurudev on Facebook: 
https://facebook.com/gurudev

Follow Gurudev on Twitter: 
https://twitter.com/srisri

Follow Gurudev on LinkedIn:

snippet.title: NEW ! C.I.D. Ep 01 | क्या Daya की गलती की वजह से गई Abhijeet की बेटी की जान? | Teaser | New Season
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to SET India: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpEhnqL0y41EpW2TvWAHD7Q?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 1: क्या Daya की गलती की वजह से गई Abhijeet की बेटी की जान?
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
During a critical rescue operation, Abhijeet tragically loses his daughter Shreya due to a minor error by Daya. Three months later, a mysterious shooting incident occurs on a metro, leaving a woman injured. How will ACP Pradyuman and his team uncover the truth behind this case?

Show Name: CID Season 2 
Episode: 1
Cast: Shivaji Satam, Dayanand Shetty, Aditya Srivastava, Ansha Sayed, Ajay Nagrath, Saumya Saraswat, Narendra Gupta, Parul Rai
Director: Shachindra Vats, Santosh Shetty
Producer: Deepak Dhar, Rajesh Chadhaa

#CID #सीआईडी #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #NewCID #Crime #NewCID #LatestCID #setindia ##NewSeason #CIDReturns #DayaReturns #AbhijeetReturns #CID2025 #CIDisBack #PurviReturns       

About CID:
-----------------
India's favourite crime thriller show is back! Abhijeet, Daya and other CID officers, led by ACP Pradyuman, join forces with forensic expert Dr Salunkhe to track down the perpetrators who have committed heinous crimes, using every small clue they can find. 'CID' stars Shivaji Satam, Dayanand Shetty, Aditya Srivastava and Narendra Gupta.

Click here to watch the full episode of CID Season 2: 
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/cid-1700000196/sniper-rifle-murderer-1090425506

snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Deeksha || Episode 01 || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Deeksha Episode 01 MCM

Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu releases its new series DEEKSHA.This new series is all about Swamy Ayyappa where our Naatu Guntala Gang wears ayyappa maala. In this new episode a funny conversation starts between mahesh and his mother later mahesh calls madhu to ask him come out to meet but the words that were used by mahesh was heard by Saradha Subba Rao and feels bad about the way how mahesh and friends turning out be. But the with help of Chinta mahesh father decided to take up ayyappa deeksha for 41 days. Watch the whole new episode of Deeksha and support this new series.

snippet.title: OP Chautala के निधन के बाद Abhay Chautala ने दिया ये बड़ा बयान | Haryana News
snippet.description:
हरियाणा के पूर्व मुख्यमंत्री ओमप्रकाश चौटाला के निधन के बाद हरियाणा के सिरसा में मातम का माहौल। अभय सिंह चौटाला के सिरसा निवास पर लोगों के आने का सिलसिला जारी। अर्जुन चौटाला सिरसा निवास से गांव चौटाला के लिए हुए रवाना। देर शाम ओम प्रकाश चौटाला का पार्थिव शरीर देर शाम गांव चौटाला में पहुंचेगा। ओम प्रकाश चौटाला के निधन की सूचना मिलने के बाद भावुक हुए समर्थक।सुबह 8 बजे से लेकर 2 बजे तक ओम प्रकाश चौटाला का पार्थिव शरीर अंतिम दर्शनों के लिए रखा जाएगा। हरियाणा और पंजाब से कई राजनेताओं के आने की संभावना। पीएम नरेंद्र मोदी , सीएम नायब सिंह सैनी, केंद्रीय मंत्री राजनाथ सिंह , केंद्रीय मंत्री मनोहर लाल , पूर्व सीएम भूपेंद्र सिंह हुडा सहित अनेक नेताओं ने अफ़सोस जाहिर किया।  
#nayabsaini #opchautala #inld #opdhankar  #digvijaychautala #dushyantchautala #jjp #haryanabreaking #abhaychautala #ajaychautala #ranjitchautala #cmsaini #bhupindersinghhooda #indianewsharyana #sirsa

snippet.title: What Happened to Amma? അമ്മയ്ക്ക് എന്താണ് സംഭവിച്ചത്?
snippet.description:
What Happened to Amma? അമ്മയ്ക്ക് എന്താണ് സംഭവിച്ചത്? #techtraveleat #family 

As you know that I have taken a break from our journey and I am at home as my mother isn't keeping well,  I had decided not to post any videos for a while. But as many are commenting and sending messages enquiring about my mother, I thought I shall show some updates like these. Thank you so much for your support and prayers.

അമ്മയ്ക്ക് വയ്യെന്നറിഞ്ഞ് യാത്രകൾക്ക് താൽക്കാലിക വിരാമമിട്ടുകൊണ്ട് ഞാൻ നാട്ടിലെത്തിയ കാര്യം എല്ലാവരും അറിഞ്ഞുകാണുമല്ലോ. ഇതിനിടയിൽ നാട്ടിൽ നിന്നുള്ള വീഡിയോകൾ ചെയ്യേണ്ട എന്നായിരുന്നു തീരുമാനമെങ്കിലും, അമ്മയുടെ വിശേഷം തിരക്കി ധാരാളമാളുകൾ കമന്റിലും മെസ്സേജിലുമൊക്കെ വരുന്നത് കാരണമാണ് ഇങ്ങനെയൊരു വീഡിയോ ചെയ്യുവാൻ തീരുമാനിച്ചത്. നിങ്ങളുടെ സപ്പോർട്ടിനും പ്രാർത്ഥനകൾക്കും നന്ദി.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Daya के हाथ का Aamras खाकर Sundar हुआ खुश | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Ke Foodies
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Jethala is worried about Sundar taking initiatives to conduct the Gokuldam Premier League 2. But on the other hand, Nattu kaka is so excited about the match that he plans to advertise their company without informing Jethala. Hence there arises the problem in getting donations for conducting the GPL. What will Jetha do now? Watch this episode to find out.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 391
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta #jethalalmemes #tmkocmemes #jethalalcomedy #food #foodies #foodie #gokuldham #fullepisode #comedyvideos #foodlover 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Ke Foodies' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cT5G12J5Crvkt1XPr2dP5iG

Daya के हाथ का Aamras खाकर Sundar हुआ खुश | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Ke Foodies

snippet.title: Decorating Home for Christmas Vlog in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video, join me as I transform our home into a cozy Christmas wonderland! This year, I’m mixing traditional holiday charm with creative DIY touches to make our decorations truly special. From twinkling fairy lights and garlands to homemade ornaments and festive centerpieces, you’ll find plenty of inspiration for your own holiday decor. In this video, I tried making a 2D Christmas tree on the wall and decorating it with ornaments.

#christmashomedecor #holidaydecorations #steffivlogs

From crafting unique tree ornaments to styling a festive mantelpiece, these ideas are perfect for families who love to get creative and embrace the holiday spirit. I hope this week’s vlog inspires you to deck your halls and enjoy a joyful holiday season. Don’t forget to like, comment, and subscribe for more festive fun. See you soon with another cheerful video!

నీ కోసం వేచుందే నా ప్రాణం
ఓ బుజ్జితల్లి

నా బుజ్జి తల్లి ..

మళ్ళీ యాళకొస్తానే

నా బుజ్జి తల్లి

ఇన్నినాళ్ళ మన దూరం

దేన్ని కానుకియ్యాలే
యెట్లా బుజ్జగించాలే
బెట్టు నువ్వు దించేలా లంచమేటి కావాలే

గాలివాన జాడేలేదే  రవ్వంతైనా నా చుట్టూ 
అయినా మునిగిపోతున్నానే దారే చూపెట్టు

నీ కోసం వేచుందే నా ప్రాణం
 ఓ బుజ్జితల్లి 
నా కోసం ఓ మాటైనా మాటాడే

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Hello!!  My Name is chef Deena from the popular Adupangarai show in Jaya TV Viewers must have seen me in Zee Tamil shows as well.  My Culinary journey as a trainee to become an Executive Chef is incredible. My experience in the culinary field is for more than fifteen years and my USP is Indian cooking !! Apart from being a TV cookery host, my experience lies mainly with being employed in some of the major star hotels across the country especially the Marriott group.

     Chef Deena Cooks is my English Youtube Channel! Practical, simple recipes are my forte and using minimal easily available ingredients is my hallmark. Rudiments of cooking and baking are taught from scratch and any amateur cook can learn to make exciting dishes by watching my channel!  Also, Cooking traditional foods, Easy cooking Recipes, Healthy Snacks, Indian curries, gravies, Baking and Millions of other homemade treats.

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4273 - Sonu ki Kundli me Prem Yog!| Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Sunn Mere Dil Episode 24 Teaser - 19th December 2024 - Har Pal Geo

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation

snippet.title: संसद में टकराव, राहुल पर आरोप मगर कहाँ है सबूत?
snippet.description:
डॉ अंबेडकर पर अमित शाह के बयान को लेकर आज संसद परिसर में बहुत कुछ हो गया। जो नहीं होना चाहिए वह भी हो गया और जो नहीं हुआ उसे लेकर भी हंगामा मचाया गया। कई तरह के दावे किए गए, आरोप लगाए गए मगर विपक्ष गृहमंत्री के इस्तीफ़े की माँग से पीछे नहीं हटा। दोनों तरफ़ से मामले दर्ज करा दिए गए हैं मगर जितने आरोप लगाए गए हैं उसके अनुपात में सबूत नहीं हैं। संसद के परिसर में तो बहुत से सीसीटीवी होंगे, अभी तक कोई आधिकारिक वीडियो सामने क्यों नहीं आया है? सवाल कई हैं, आप हमारा वीडियो आख़िर तक देखिए।

snippet.title: KARATE KID: LEGENDS - Official Trailer (HD)
snippet.description:
Two branches. One tree.
 
Jackie Chan, Ben Wang, and Ralph Macchio star in Karate Kid: Legends - exclusively in movie theatres May 30. #KarateKidMovie

Learn more: https://www.karatekid.movie
 
Subscribe to Sony Pictures for exclusive content: https://www.youtube.com/@sonypictures

Follow Us On Social:
https://www.facebook.com/TheKarateKid/
https://twitter.com/karatekidmovie
https://www.instagram.com/karatekidmovie/
https://www.tiktok.com/@karatekidmovie

In Karate Kid: Legends, after a family tragedy, kung fu prodigy Li Fong (Ben Wang) is uprooted from his home in Beijing and forced to move to New York City with his mother. Li struggles to let go of his past as he tries to fit in with his new classmates, and although he doesn't want to fight, trouble seems to find him everywhere. When a new friend needs his help, Li enters a karate competition – but his skills alone aren't enough. Li's kung fu teacher Mr. Han (Jackie Chan) enlists original Karate Kid Daniel LaRusso (Ralph Macchio) for help, and Li learns a new way to fight, merging their two styles into one for the ultimate martial arts showdown.

Directed by: Jonathan Entwistle   
 
Written by: Rob Lieber    

Produced by: Karen Rosenfelt
          
Executive Producers:
Jenny Hinkey
Ralph Macchio

Cast:
Jackie Chan and Ralph Macchio
Ben Wang
Joshua Jackson
Sadie Stanley
Ming-Na Wen

This film is not yet rated by The Motion Picture Association. For future rating information, please visit https://www.filmratings.com. Credits not final

Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.
